OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1780830170
OL,3,CTwo people taken to hospital after
OL,4,Cdouble stabbing in Stoke
OL,6,FPolice have made two arrests after a
OL,7,Fdouble stabbing, where two other
OL,8,Fpeople were injured.
OL,10,FOfficers have detained two Stoke-on-
OL,11,FTrent men after a 'large fight' on The
OL,12,FStrand, in Longton. A third suspect
OL,13,Fremains at large.
OL,15,FThe drama unfolded at 11.45am on
OL,16,FSaturday, June 6.
OL,18,FA Staffordshire Police spokesman said:
OL,19,F"Two men have been arrested following
OL,20,Fa fight where two people suffered stab
OL,21,Fwounds.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
