OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1780830170
OL,3,CTwo people taken to hospital after
OL,4,Cdouble stabbing in Stoke
OL,6,F"We were called to The Strand
OL,7,Ffollowing a report that a group of
OL,8,Fpeople were fighting in the street.
OL,9,FThe men were then seen running off
OL,10,Ftowards the market in the direction of
OL,11,FFenton.
OL,13,F"Officers attended the scene alongside
OL,14,Fparamedics from West Midlands
OL,15,FAmbulance Service and set up a cordon.
OL,16,FTwo men were found with multiple
OL,17,Fsuspected stab wounds and have been
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1780830170
OL,3,CTwo people taken to hospital after
OL,4,Cdouble stabbing in Stoke
OL,6,F"Two people from Stoke-on-Trent have
OL,7,Fbeen arrested. One man, aged 28, has
OL,8,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of wounding
OL,9,Fwith intent. Another man, aged 22, has
OL,10,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of grievous
OL,11,Fbodily harm with intent.
OL,13,F"One man, who may have also been
OL,14,Finvolved, ran off after it happened.
OL,15,FHe is described as white, bald, around
OL,16,F5ft 8ins tall, roughly middle-aged,
OL,17,Fand wearing black joggers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
