CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1780830170
OL,3,CTwo people taken to hospital after
OL,4,Cdouble stabbing in Stoke
OL,6,F"He was seen on King Street shortly
OL,7,Fafter the incident took place.
OL,8,FOfficers are speaking to businesses in
OL,9,Fthe area to look at CCTV and are keen
OL,10,Fto speak to anyone who may be able to
OL,11,Fhelp with our investigation."
OL,13,FWitnesses can call the police on 101,
OL,14,Fquoting incident number 281 of 6 June,
OL,15,For call Crimestoppers, anonymously, on
OL,16,F0800 555111.
